    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "You can attach these light-brown leather flaps adorned with gold stitching to a breastplate or even clothing to protect your upper legs in battle. They give you the freedom to move your body to its limit without worrying about exposing yourself to a hit. While wearing the *tasset of flexibility*, you gain a +1 item bonus to Acrobatics checks.",
        "level": 4,
